OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBreezy with occasional rain
OL,6,Facross many northwestern areas today.
OL,7,FElsewhere, rather cloudy but mainly
OL,8,Fdry throughout the morning though some
OL,9,Fpatchy rain possible across windward
OL,10,Fcoasts and hills. Turning brighter
OL,11,Ffrom the south during the afternoon
OL,12,Fwith some sunny spells.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy with further
OL,15,Fspells of rain across parts of the
OL,16,Fnorth and west. Clear spells elsewhere
OL,17,Fallowing some mist and fog to develop,
OL,18,Fespecially across southern England.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
