OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FFurther spells of rain
OL,6,Facross Scotland, Northern Ireland, and
OL,7,Fparts of Wales and northern England.
OL,8,FElsewhere, early fog clearing leading
OL,9,Fto a very mild day with plenty of
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
